ce</Summary><LongDescription>Contains time account balance information which allows external systems like Payroll access to the data. You can use this information to enrich the employee's pay slip with time off data.</LongDescription><sap:tagcollection><sap:tag>Employee Central (EC)</sap:tag><sap:tag>EC - Time Off</sap:tag><sap:tag>Results List Not Supported</sap:tag></sap:tagcollection></Documentation></EntitySet><EntitySet Name="RBPRole" EntityType="SFOData.RBPRole" sap:label="RBPRole" sap:creatable="false" sap:updatable="false" sap:upsertable="true" sap:deletable="true"><Documentation><Summary>RBPRole</Summary><LongDescription>This entity lists the permitted roles in an Roles Based Permissions (RPB) system. You can use this entity to query the list of roles that exist in the system. The roles are only created through the user interface. You can use this API to grant a role to a user.</LongDescription><sap:tagcollection><sap:tag>Foundation/Platform (PLT)</sap:tag><sap:tag>PLT - Role Based Permissions</sap:tag></sap:tagcollection></Documentation></EntitySet><EntitySet Name="FODivision" EntityType="SFOData.FODivision" sap:label="Division" sap:creatable="true" sap:updatable="true" sap:upsertable="true" sap:deletable="true"><Documentation><Summary>FODivision</Summary><LongDescription>This is a foundation object that describes a particular division in a company structure.</LongDescription><sap:tagcollection><sap:tag>Employee Central (EC)</sap:tag><sap:tag>EC - Foundation/Organization</sap:tag></sap:tagcollection></Documentation></EntitySet><EntitySet Name="PerGlobalInfoURY" EntityType="SFOData.PerGlobalInfoURY" sap:label="Global Information" sap:creatable="false" sap:updatable="false" sap:upsertable="true" sap:deletable="false"><Documentation><Summary></Summary><LongDescription></LongDescription><sap:tagcollection><sap:tag>Employee Central (EC)</sap:tag></sap:tagcollection></Documentation></EntitySet><EntitySet Name="FOJobClassLocalCAN" EntityType="SFOData.FOJobClassLo